#priorTo SyncAndPushGlinda NeatenKitchen

#NOW 2008-03-04 14:53:45

In the post office today, I turned my back.  Ethan had sat down on the
ground to read his snap circuits book, and Isaac had come up and
kicked him.  I told Isaac that when we got home, I was giving
Lightning McQueen a time-out.  Isaac spent the rest of the time there
trying to make sure I saw him spitting.

I hadn't brought things for Ethan and Isaac to do, and that was my
fault.  I can't expect Isaac to understand what the errand was
about--it needed a stand-in, and I hadn't created one.

package org.apache.commons.collections.bag;

import static org.junit.Assert.assertEquals;
import static org.junit.Assert.assertTrue;

import org.apache.commons.collections.Bag;

public class TestHashBag_forTalk extends TestCase {
    public void testBagAdd() {
        Bag bag = new HashBag();
        bag.add("A");
        assertTrue("Should contain 'A'", bag.contains("A"));
        assertEquals("Should have count of 1", 1, bag.getCount("A"));
        bag.add("A");
        assertTrue("Should contain 'A'", bag.contains("A"));
        assertEquals("Should have count of 2", 2, bag.getCount("A"));
        bag.add("B");
        assertTrue(bag.contains("A"));
        assertTrue(bag.contains("B"));
    }
}

ETHAN

1) Have you seen anyone in the state that Ethan is now?
2) Have you noticed a change in the last month?
3) How hard is it to send the notes home?
4) Is Ethan respectful of his teachers?  Does he threaten them?
5) Does Ethan talk about things that are bothering him at home?
6) What are Ethan's favorite times of day?
7) How is Ethan doing in the afternoons?
8) When does Ethan spend the most time with other kids?
9) What have you noticed in writing and fine motor control?
10) Things that work for me:
  a) Who controls your body?
  b) Being honest about mad feelings
  c) Setting clear consequences
11) Do you know of any good psychiatrists?

ISAAC

1) How has it been going on the potty lately?
2) What are Isaac's favorite things to do at school?
3) How does Isaac do when he's angry?
4) Do they know about Ethan?
5) Who are Isaac's favorite friends in the class?
6) Have you noticed Isaac's writing?
7) How much does Isaac suck his thumb?
8) What does Isaac like to talk about?
